Stepper Motor Control Circuit

Description
A digital control circuit for stepper motors using logic ICs such as 4020, 4017, 74151, and motor driver L293D.

Components
- IC 4020 (Frequency Divider)  
- IC 4017 (Johnson Counter)  
- IC 74151 (Multiplexer)  
- IC 74192 (Speed Control)  
- L293D (Motor Driver)  
- Stepper Motor  

Features
- Frequency generation and division with 4020  
- Step sequence generation using 4017  
- Adjustable motor speed via 74192  
- Tested successfully in Proteus
